\cpter{Structure}

An verll picture fr ding PD
\begin{enumerte}[nsep]
    \item At te very beginning f PD, find  disserttin templte, nd cmplete te verll structure f te disserttin.
    \item Wenever find gd ides nd tugts, stuff tem int te crrespnding sectins.
    \item Wenever strt t develp r implement  metd, express te metd nd its implementtin in te disserttin first, cntinuusly imprve te expressin until ll te prcedures being full explined nd understd, ten implement te metd, nd ten iterte between te expressin nd implementtin prcesses.
\end{enumerte}
An verll picture fr ding reserc
\begin{enumerte}[nsep]
    \item Reserc = ide + vlidtin + delivery (presenttin r pper t cmmunicte ides)
    \item Te gretest ides re (literlly) wrtless if yu keep tem t yurself \citep{peytn2004write}.
    \item Gl: t cnvey yur ide frm yur ed t yur reder's ed; t infect te mind f yur reder wit yur ide, like  virus.
    \item Te wrng wy t d reserc: ide $\t$ d reserc $\t$ write pper.
    \item Te crrect wy t d reserc: ide $\t$ write pper $\t$ d reserc.
        \begin{itemize}[nsep]
            \item Write  pper, nd give  tlk, but ny ide, n mtter w insignificnt it my seem t yu.
            \item Writing is te wy t rigrusly develp te ide in te first plce.
            \item Being frced t be cler nd fcused.
            \item Crystllises unknwn nd missing spects.
            \item Ppers re like wine: tey need time t mture.
        \end{itemize}
\end{enumerte}
An verll picture fr pper writing
\begin{enumerte}[nsep]
    \item Ask wt is te mst imprtnt ide tt yu wnt t cnvey t yur reder?
    \item Determine  tesis sttement t functin like  seed frm wic yur pper nd yur ides will grw.
    \item Decmpse te pper t: skeletn (structure) $+$ bdy prts (cntent) $+$ rteries (delivery nd ide flw).
    \item Build  skeletn t supprt te bdy f pper: title + bstrct + intrductin wit tree mves + metd nd results wit subsectin edings + cnclusin.
    \item Stuff ec bdy prt t cnvey te min ide trug reding literture, extrcting useful cntent, nd expressing yur wn tugts.
    \item Implnt rteries int ec bdy prt t smt te ide flw vi resning, refining, nd mking trnsitins.
    \item Revise te pper t mke sure tt te wle prcess is n rgnic ne --  nturl prgressin frm  seed t  full-blwn pper were tere re direct, fmilil reltinsips between ll f te ides in te pper.
\end{enumerte}
